A highly detailed, vibrant oil painting depicting a worn, oversized grey hoodie radiating a gentle, comforting warmth. A small, shimmering spectral aura outlines the hoodie, subtly illuminating a weary, slightly inebriated grey wolf wearing the hoodie, standing in a dimly lit tavern. The background is blurred with hints of wood and tankards. Style: Fantasy Illustration, warm color palette, cinematic lighting.